Item Name: Business Catalyst Training class in San Francisco
Item Description:
February 26-27, 2013

The two day Business Catalyst course will help you grow your online business. Each day also includes time for one-on-one consulting so we can discuss your specific BC site and goals. We love to answer your questions, so make sure you come prepared.

We will provide you with:

  • Continental Breakfast
  • Catered Lunch
  • Laptop to use during classes
  • Demo website

Join us in San Francisco at the Adobe offices and let our experts help you get the most out of your online business.

To learn more about our BC training courses, please visit our BC training pages.

$495 per day.
